  <description><![CDATA[<p>This stunning and centrally located hotel has been beautifully designed in traditional Alpine style and surrounded by magnificent views of the Mount Rosa. Run directly by the owners, it guarantees an excellent service and a special attention to detail. The cuisine is also a key part of the hotel’s reputation and the fine dining restaurant specialises in local dishes as well as international specialities accompanied by a great selection of magnificent wines. The desserts are prepared by the Patisserie du Relais, the hotel’s own fine patisserie. The nearest lift is 8 minutes' walk (800m) away.</p>]]></description>
